					<h3>Moving to Newcastle</h3>

					<img src="http://www.101-charger.com/wallpapers/jeux/angleterre/Tyne-Bridge-and-Swing-Bridge-Newcastle-Upon-Tyne-United-Kingdom.jpg" width="500px" alt="Newcastle upon Tyne" style="margin-top:30px;">

